1|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/><ref name="Meteonetwork2">[http://forum.meteonetwork.it/meteorologia/134165-reports-from-spain-58.html Reports from Spain, page 58]</ref> | [[Montoro]] | August 10, 2012 |- | {{convert|46|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Abc.es"/> | [[Jaén, Spain|Jaén]] | July 8, 1939 |- | {{convert|46|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="AEMET2"/> | Llanos de Aridane, [[La Palma]] | August 20, 1953 |- | {{convert|46|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Meteonetwork3"/> | [[Écija]] | August 10, 2012 |- | {{convert|46|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Meteonetwork1">[http://forum.meteonetwork.it/meteorologia/134165-reports-from-spain-56.html Reports from Spain, page 56]</ref> | Mengíbar | August 10, 2012 |- |- | {{convert|45.9|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/> | Seville | August 11, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.8|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/> | [[La Rambla, Córdoba|La Rambla]] | August 10, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.9|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Meteonetwork2"/> | Ciudad Jardín, Córdoba | August 11, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.6|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/> | Córdoba | July 20, 1967 |- | {{convert|45.6|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/> | Córdoba | July 22 and 24, 1995 |- | {{convert|45.5|°C|abbr=on}} | [[Albacete]] | August 31, 1903 |- | {{convert|45.5|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="AEMET2"/> | [[La Oliva]] | July 4, 1994 |- | {{convert|45.5|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Meteonetwork1"/> | El Carpio | August 9, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.4|°C|abbr=on}} | Seville | July 23, 1995 |- | {{convert|45.4|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/><ref name="Meteonetwork1"/> | Córdoba | July 17, 1978 and August 11, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.3|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="Meteonetwork1"/> | [[Úbeda]] | August 9, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.3|°C|abbr=on}} | [[Arahal]] | August 11, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.3|°C|abbr=on}} | Jaén | August 9, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.2|°C|abbr=on}} | [[Colmenar, Málaga|Colmenar]] | August 11, 2012 |- | {{convert|45.2|°C|abbr=on}}<ref name="New record meteo"/><ref name="Meteonetwork