{{DEFAULTSORT:Extreme temperatures in Spain}} [[Category:Climate of Spain]] [[Category:Climatology]] [[Category:Spain-related lists]] [[Category:Lists of superlatives]] [[Category:Weather-related lists]]

The following is a '''list of [[tautonym]]s''': [[zoological]] names of species consisting of two identical words (the [[genus|generic name]] and the [[specific name (zoology)|specific name]] have the same spelling). Such names are allowed in [[zoology]], but not in [[botany]], where the two parts of the name of a species must differ (though differences as small as one letter are permitted, as in the [[jujube]] (''Ziziphus zizyphus'')).
{{Expand list|date=August 2008}}
