at *''[[Klipspringer|Oreotragus oreotragus]]'' <small>Zimmermann, 1783</small> — klipspringer *''[[Guinea baboon|Papio papio]]'' <small>Desmarest, 1820</small> — Guinea baboon *''[[Red giant flying squirrel|Petaurista petaurista]]'' <small>Pallas, 1766</small> — red giant flying squirrel *''[[Harbour porpoise|Phocoena phocoena]]'' <small>Linnaeus, 1758</small> — harbor porpoise, harbour porpoise *''[[Common pipistrelle|Pipistrellus pipistrellus]]'' <small>Schreber, 1774</small> — common pipistrelle *''[[White-faced saki|Pithecia pithecia]]'' <small>Linnaeus, 1766</small> — white-faced saki *''[[Southern pudu|Pudu pudu = Pudu puda]]'' <small>Molina, 1782</small> — southern pudu *''[[Black rat|Rattus rattus]]'' <small>Linnaeus, 1758</small> — roof rat, black rat *''[[Southern reedbuck|Redunca redunca]]'' <small>Pallas, 1767</small> — common reedbuck *''[[Chamois|Rupicapra rupicapra]]'' <small>Linnaeus, 1758</small> — Alpine chamois, chamois *''[[Naked-rumped pouched bat|Saccolaimus saccolaimus]]'' <small>Temminck, 1838</small> — naked-rumped pouched bat *''[[Snow leopard|Uncia uncia = Panthera uncia]]'' <small>Schreber, 1775</small> — snow leopard *''[[Vicuña|Vicugna vicugna]]'' <small>Molina, 1782</small> — vicugna, vicuña *''[[Red fox|Vulpes vulpes]]'' <small>Linnaeus, 1758</small> — red fox {{-}}
